3Cp\u003E\nAnd how to test my mod? I had to close and relaunch the game ? Or theres is any trick to \u0022refresh\u0022 my mod without opening the game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-14T03:24:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224198561\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022210599\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221668393375\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022171609\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Albert7df\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n47 minutes ago, Albert7df said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd how to test my mod? I had to close and relaunch the game ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes,\u00A0 or at least this is what I have always done.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224198561\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022210599\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221668393375\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022171609\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Albert7df\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n47 minutes ago, Albert7df said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr theres is any trick to \u0022refresh\u0022 my mod without opening the game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know of any way, but maybe someone will stop by and enlighten both of us.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":